{"tid":736804,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"曾焯文：英國新外相妻來自中共；軍情六處曾頒色戒　","createTime":"2018-07-10T13:27:33.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-10T15:36:12.000Z","uid":53379,"like":14,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"db8be8975704b6b3b0932213dde74d9453b94e31","tid":736804,"uid":53379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-10T13:27:34.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>曾焯文：英國新外相妻來自中共；軍情六處曾頒色戒　</strong></span><br />\nChapman Chen: New UK Foreign Secretary&rsquo;s Wife Comes from China; MI6 had Warned of China Honey-traps<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.localpresshk.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/Jeremy-and-Wen.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.localpresshk.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F07%2FJeremy-and-Wen.jpg&h=f8a3e5c3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n英國首相文翠珊周一委任留歐派衞生大臣侯俊偉（Jeremy Hunt）出任外相，接替約翰遜 (Boris Johnson)。侯俊偉之妻Lucia郭來自中共西安。侯俊偉身為外相，兼領軍情六處。軍情六處一五年告知當時首相金馬倫：中共經部署「數百名美女」，色誘成員官員及其家屬。同年保守黨會議上，侯俊偉話其妻是中國人，自己認識中國好深，督促英國人要學習中國人一樣勤力。工黨女議員古德曼（Helen Goodman）隨後於Twitter話，「既然中國咁好，何解侯俊偉的老婆要來英國？」（結果古德曼備受批評種族歧視，卒之刪除留言，並向侯俊偉道歉。）<br />\n香港名作家陶傑今日用英文寫道：「英國外交過去常見的專業做法乃係：官員一旦與中國人或俄羅斯人結婚，外交部就會要求其辭職，以便其與心目中偉大的西貢小姐或蝴蝶夫人做對異國情鴛。」（<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/tokit.channel/photos/a.533448593394335.1073741825.272574169481780/2041075162631663/?type=3）\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Ftokit.channel%2Fphotos%2Fa.533448593394335.1073741825.272574169481780%2F2041075162631663%2F%3Ftype%3D3%EF%BC%89&d=eR1TBwj6C9DhNxCubXnTRl0Hwm5JNK6yt%2FgZtp%2B4HOw%3D&h=5f757ab7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/tokit.channel/photos/a.533448593394335.1073741825.272574169481780/2041075162631663/?type=3）</a><br />\n<br />\n約翰遜因不滿政府軟脫歐政策，周一（九日）宣布請辭。侯俊偉五十一歲，英女皇遠親，為英國數一數二富有政治家。財富主要來自其自創線上教育公司Hotcourses。零八年於英國華威（Warwick）Hotcourses活動中，結識細其十一年的Lucia郭，一見鍾情，一年後在西安舉行傳統中國婚禮，至今育有三名仔女。<br />\n<br />\n一六年九月，英國首相文翠珊到杭州參加G20峰會，英國政府安全專家向隨行官員下「色戒」，要其小心中國間諜美人計。<br />\n<br />\n根據軍情六處一五年一份最高機密備忘錄：「中國特務越來越主動積極接近皇家政府前成員，包括安全及情報機構。他們特別留意定期到中國大陸同香港公幹的前官員。」（<a href=\"https://www.mirror.co.uk/news/uk-news/china-using-sexy-honeytrap-women-6747631\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mirror.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fuk-news%2Fchina-using-sexy-honeytrap-women-6747631&d=eR1TBwj6C9DhNxCubXnTRl0Hwm5JNK6yt%2FgZtp%2B4HOw%3D&h=e9819d53\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.mirror.co.uk/news/uk-news/china-using-sexy-honeytrap-women-6747631</a>）<br />\n圖為侯俊偉暨妻小一一年與溫家寶合照。Photo credit: Mirror.<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.localpresshk.com/2018/07/jeremy-hunt-mi6/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.localpresshk.com%2F2018%2F07%2Fjeremy-hunt-mi6%2F&d=eR1TBwj6C9DhNxCubXnTRl0Hwm5JNK6yt%2FgZtp%2B4HOw%3D&h=d8abd9e4\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.localpresshk.com/2018/07/jeremy-hunt-mi6/</a>"},{"pid":"52dbda1ed5eeb63ae7d7db9e11e3de126ce151ad","tid":736804,"uid":53379,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-10T13:28:31.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/tokit.channel/photos/a.533448593394335.1073741825.272574169481780/2041075162631663/?type=3&amp;theater\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Ftokit.channel%2Fphotos%2Fa.533448593394335.1073741825.272574169481780%2F2041075162631663%2F%3Ftype%3D3%26theater&d=eR1TBwj6C9DhNxCubXnTRl0Hwm5JNK6yt%2FgZtp%2B4HOw%3D&h=23a46290\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/tokit.channel/photos/a.533448593394335.1073741825.272574169481780/2041075162631663/?type=3&amp;theater</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg1-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/36889518_2041075165964996_5956901407968722944_n.jpg?_nc_cat=0&amp;oh=0ee3aac9c78bf646e8bfed5de898e90a&amp;oe=5BD3C767\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg1-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F36889518_2041075165964996_5956901407968722944_n.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D0%26oh%3D0ee3aac9c78bf646e8bfed5de898e90a%26oe%3D5BD3C767&h=bb181bd9&s=